  <brief_title>Prevalence of Pancreatic Anomalies of Patients With a 1st Degree Familial History of Pancreatic Adenocarcinoma</brief_title>
  <acronym>PAPAFA</acronym>
  <official_title>Prevalence, With Medical Imaging, of the Parenchymatous and/or Ductal Pancreatic Anomalies of Patients With a 1st Degree Familial History of Pancreatic Adenocarcinoma</official_title>
